			<p>Oh man. I want that for breakfast. Now.</p>
<p>I need someone to tell me what to make for dinner tonight. Thanks!</p>
<p>I, too, am a pasta freak of the first order.<br />
My daughter is on a gluten free diet and that challenge first crushed me but I have found a wonderful rice pasta company that is almost as good as the &#8220;real&#8221; thing. Tinkyada.</p>
